    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The engine runs and the car is drivable, but you may notice some minor fluid leaks and a suspension that feels a bit loose, suggesting some maintenance will be required in the near future. Externally, the paint has faded in several spots and there are visible dings and scratches consistent with regular use. The interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and some of the plastic trim pieces are cracked. This is an ideal choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point who doesn't mind putting in some work to improve its overall state.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
