    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this well-maintained vehicle, which exemplifies a harmonious balance of performance and value. Meticulously cared for by its previous owner, the automobile features a clean, preserved interior and a powertrain that delivers consistent, reliable performance. Each component has been professionally evaluated to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and aesthetic appeal. This offering represents an excellent opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a dependable, high-quality vehicle without compromise.",
      "price": 33800.0,
