    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and meticulous care. The exterior retains a vibrant, deep shine, showing only the minor, superficial signs of road use typical of a well-loved daily driver. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and well-preserved; the upholstery is firm and free of any significant wear or odors, and every electronic feature\u2014from the crisp sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, characterized by a smooth-idling engine and precise gear shifts. It has been strictly maintained with a documented service history, ensuring it drives with the same confidence and stability it did years ago. This is a dependable, high-quality vehicle for someone who appreciates a car that has been treated with respect.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
